arts.ttl: Japan forwards Nakamura and Ito score as Reims wins 3-1 at Angers in French league
arts.sum: Midtable Lyon rallied to win 2-1 at Toulouse, with forward Malick Fofana scoring the winner five minutes into stoppage time. Japan forwards Keito Nakamura and Junya Ito scored first-half goals to help Reims win 3-1 at Angers and move up to fourth place in the French league on Sunday.

arts.ttl: Angers set for 21st century Ligue 1 milestone
